  "status": "Review",
  "summary": "There are multiple token standards on Ethereum chain currently. This EIP introduces a concept of cross-standard interoperability by creating a service that allows [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) tokens to be upgraded to [ERC-223](./eip-223.md) tokens anytime. [ERC-223](./eip-223.md) tokens can be converted back to [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) version without any restrictions to avoid any problems with backwards compatibility and allow different standards to co-exist and become interoperable and interchangeable. In order to perform the conversion, a user must deposit tokens of one standard to the Converter contract and it will automatically send tokens of another standard back.",
  "title": "Token Converter"
}